        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your connection to the First World is strong. Whenever you meet a fey creature in a social situation, you can immediately attempt a Diplomacy check to [[/act make-an-impression]] on that creature rather than needing to converse for 1 minute. You take a –4 circumstance penalty to the check. If you fail, you can engage in 1 minute of conversation and attempt a new check at the end of that time rather than accepting the failure or critical failure result. In addition, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to both Perception checks and saving throws against fey.</p>"
